                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#what-is-gift-aid" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #what-is-gift-aid" ga-event-label=" Gift Aid  What is Gift Aid?">What is Gift Aid?</a>
                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#what-is-gift-aid" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #what-is-gift-aid" ga-event-label=" Gift Aid  How does it work?">How does it work?</a>
                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#making-sure-youve-paid-enough-tax-to-use-gift-aid" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #making-sure-youve-paid-enough-tax-to-use-gift-aid" ga-event-label=" Gift Aid  Paying Enough Tax">Paying Enough Tax</a>
                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#making-sure-youve-paid-enough-tax-to-use-gift-aid" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #making-sure-youve-paid-enough-tax-to-use-gift-aid" ga-event-label=" Gift Aid  Higher rate tax">Higher rate tax</a>
                      </div>
