<hr data-drupal-selector="edit-horizontal-rule-02" id="edit-horizontal-rule-02" class="webform-horizontal-rule" />
<div id="edit-your-declaration" class="js-form-item form-item js-form-type-webform-markup form-type-webform-markup js-form-item-your-declaration form-item-your-declaration form-no-label">
        <h3>Your Gift Aid Declaration</h3><p><strong>When selecting Gift Aid you are declaring that:</strong></p><ul><li>You are donating your own money and the funds have not come from anyone else including family members or from an office or bucket collection.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</li><li>The money you are donating is not the proceeds from the sale of goods or services, or the sale of tickets.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</li><li>You have not received something in return for this donation, such as an entry ticket to an event or a raffle ticket.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</li><li>The money that we claim back from HMRC as part of the Gift Aid scheme will be treated as unrestricted funds and used to support our general work, even if your original donation was made towards a specific project.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Please read the statement below and tick the box to make your Gift Aid declaration:</strong></p>
        </div>
<fieldset data-drupal-selector="edit-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f" id="edit-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f--wrapper" class="checkboxes--wrapper fieldgroup form-composite webform-composite-visible-title required js-webform-type-checkboxes webform-type-checkboxes js-form-item form-item js-form-wrapper form-wrapper">
      <legend>
    <span class="fieldset-legend js-form-required form-required">I want to Gift Aid my donation and any donations I make in the future or have made in the past 4 years, to WWF-UK. I am a UK taxpayer and understand that if I pay less income tax in the current tax year than the amount of Gift Aid claimed on my donations it is my responsibility to pay any difference. Gift Aid is claimed by WWF-UK from the tax you pay for the current tax year.</span>
  </legend>
  <div class="fieldset-wrapper">
                <div id="edit-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f" class="js-webform-checkboxes webform-options-display-one-column form-checkboxes"><div class="input_group input_group--checkbox_radio js-form-item form-item js-form-type-checkbox form-type-checkbox js-form-item-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f-yes form-item-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f-yes">
        <input data-drupal-selector="edit-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f-yes" type="checkbox" id="edit-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f-yes" name="i_want_to_gift_aid_my_donation_and_any_donations_i_make_in_the_f[Yes]" value="Yes" class="form-checkbox" />

        <label for="edit-i-want-to-gift-aid-my-donation-and-any-donations-i-make-in-the-f-yes" class="option">Yes</label>
      </div>
</div>

          </div>
</fieldset>

<hr data-drupal-selector="edit-horizontal-rule-01" id="edit-horizontal-rule-01" class="webform-horizontal-rule" />
<section data-drupal-selector="edit-your-privacy" aria-describedby="edit-your-privacy--description" id="edit-your-privacy" class="js-form-item form-item js-form-wrapper form-wrapper webform-section">
        <h3 class="webform-section-title">Your Privacy</h3>
    <div class="webform-section-wrapper">
              <div class="description"><div id="edit-your-privacy--description" class="webform-element-description">Your personal details will only be used to provide you with the goods or services you've requested or information you'd reasonably expect or have agreed to.</div>

<div id="edit-your-privacy--more" class="js-webform-element-more webform-element-more">
  <div class="webform-element-more--link"><a role="button" href="#edit-your-privacy--more--content">To see what this may include read more.</a></div>
  <div id="edit-your-privacy--more--content" class="webform-element-more--content"><p>WWF-UK (including WWF-UK Trading Ltd) will collect data from you to process your donation, provide you with the goods/services you've requested, personalise your supporter experience, or provide you with fundraising and marketing materials (including by post and telephone unless you've told us not to).<br>
<br>
Personal details collected this way will only be used to provide you with information you'd reasonably expect or have agreed to, and in accordance with our <a aria-controls="foo" href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/privacy-and-data-protection" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>. In limited circumstances, this may include using your data, in combination with public data sources, to analyse, research and profile our supporter base, so that our communications with you are more tailored and therefore cost-effective.<br>
<br>
You can object to this processing at any time by contacting our Supporter Care team on 01483 426333 or supportercare@wwf.org.uk. We'll keep your personal details safe and won't share them with any other organisations unless they're working on our behalf, or if we're required to by law.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
            
          </div>
</section>
<div id="edit-markup-01" class="js-form-item form-item js-form-type-webform-markup form-type-webform-markup js-form-item-markup-01 form-item-markup-01 form-no-label">
        <p>If, at any time, you’d like us to change the way we contact you, please visit wwf.org.uk/change-contact or call Supporter Care on 01483 426333. For full details on how we collect, use and store your personal information, please see our <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/privacy-and-data-protection">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>

